lead_paragraph: Denver Broncos linebacker Brandon Marshall became the latest athlete to kneel during the U.S. national anthem in a protest against social injustice before his team's game against the Carolina Panthers on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Denver Broncos' Marshall Kneels in Protest During National Anthem
